## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of the issue due to the complexity and variability of individual experiences. Additionally, some sources may not have the most current data, and the impact of recent policy changes on this issue may not be fully reflected. Further research is needed to explore the nuanced effects of parental incarceration across different demographics and to evaluate the effectiveness of interventions designed to mitigate these impacts.

